    },
    "description": "4-stage island area restoration sequence over 5s. Stage1(0-1s): gray→color. Stage2(1-2.5s): details/particles appear. Stage3(2.5-4s): glow pulse bloom. Stage4(4-5s): settle to final state. Uses child node paths: ColorOverlay, GlowLayer, DetailLayer."
  }
